                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-190-victim1335 t18180401-190-viclabel1075"></join>. On the 15th of February I was going up <placeName id="t18180401-190-crimeloc1076">Brick-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180401-190-crimeloc1076" type="placeName" value="Brick-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180401-190-crimeloc1076" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-190-off1073 t18180401-190-crimeloc1076"></join> with my wife, and was stopped by a mob in the road. The prisoner was on my right side - He snatched my seal and key, and ran off. I pursued him; four or five of the gang followed me. I returned, and gave information at the Office - He was taken the next day. I picked him out from among several others,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181804010051"></xptr>and am sure he is the man. He was exactly under the gas-light.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was not there.</p>
